leader skill.name: 聖天刃の霊力

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１６連ダメージ＆味方のＢＢゲージを超絶増加＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力をかなりアップ・ＢＣ・ＨＣ出現率をかなりアップ・攻撃力に応じて防御力をアップ
sbb.name: オルタナティヴ・シン

ubb.desc: 敵全体に超強力な闇属性２１連ダメージ＆味方のＢＢゲージを満タンにする＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力・防御力を超絶アップ・攻撃ＢＢの威力を超絶アップ
ubb.name: 神双極刃『イシュリオン』

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性９連ダメージ＆味方全体に１ターン、被ダメージを半分に軽減＆３ターン、防御力をかなりアップ・被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
bb.name: モーヴフォール

dictionary.description: A swordsman who lived during the dawn of Elgaia. Laberd was left an orphan after he was rescued from Grand Gaia, and spent a good portion of his life living in solitude. As luck would have it, one day an old swordsman by the name of Dolk appeared before him and forced Laberd to learn the art of fencing. Dolk was so impressed with Laberd's natural talent that he considered relinquishing a certain title to him later on. However, Laberd would suddenly leave his master's side claiming that the path they were both pursuing was different.
dictionary.fusion:
Learning fencing is not hard.
I just had a problem accepting
there was no place for me
to put it to use.
dictionary.summon:
You use me, I use you.
As long as we're helping the weak,
it doesn't matter.

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの防御力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ
leader skill.name: 絶神の聖域

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１２連ダメージ＆味方全体に１ターン、被ダメージを半分に軽減＆３ターン、防御力をかなりアップ・被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
bb.name: モーヴディケイ

dictionary.description: A swordsman who lived during the dawn of Elgaia. Unlike his master, who sought a path towards the purity of swordsmanship, Laberd wanted his skills with the sword to serve a practical purpose in the world. It was for this reason he sought employment with the provisional government. At first, the government officials kept their distance from him, as his character was too obscure and hard to decipher. However, once they learned the extent of his skills, they assigned him to work from the shadows under a special team. Once the Randall Guard was established shortly afterwards, Laberd joined their ranks as well while continuing his previous missions.
dictionary.evolution:
Though my master saw beyond the limit
of Veda fencing, he never taught me.
That's why I keep studying on my own.
dictionary.fusion:
I don't think power is everything.
But it is a necessity in every era.
That's why I must keep myself strong.
dictionary.summon:
Names are meaningless.
I will help the weak with my power.
Even if my hands are stained...

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの防御力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージを少し増加
leader skill.name: 絶神の聖咆

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１５連ダメージ＆確率で攻撃力を１ターン大幅に低下＆味方全体に１ターン、被ダメージを半分に軽減＆３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
sbb.name: 影ヴェーダ流穿剣『ゼクウ』

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１５連ダメージ＆味方全体に１ターン、被ダメージを半分に軽減＆３ターン、防御力をかなりアップ・被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
bb.name: モーヴスカージ

dictionary.description: Although Laberd had joined the Randall Guard, he still felt like he didn't belong anywhere. Little did he know that a demon would suddenly appear while he was lost in his thoughts though. His inventive commander in chief gave him the orders to proceed, while a tactician shared the strategy to be implemented on the field. Laberd then learned that his role would be that of landing a fatal blow on the demon alongside the commander's younger sister. Expressionless as always, Laberd carried out his duty, remaining with the Guard a while longer after the demon had been defeated.
dictionary.evolution:
Master...I'm grateful to you.
You believed my living corpse
could surpass the power of demons.
dictionary.fusion:
The only ones I've ever served
are you and Rouche.
Haha, the memories...
dictionary.summon:
A Veda fencing master has a pupil.
But I chose my own path.
A path with troublesome companions...

extra skill.desc: 防御貫通効果を無効＆被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージを増加
extra skill.name: 継がれしは剣魂

leader skill.name: 狂呪皇の魔神域

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１７連ダメージ＆確率で攻撃力を１ターン大幅に低下＆味方全体に１ターン、被ダメージを半分に軽減＆３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
sbb.name: 影ヴェーダ流終剣『ムゴウ』

ubb.name: 冥魂の紫封剣

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１０連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ・確率でスパーククリティカルが発生＆味方のＢＢゲージを大幅に増加
bb.name: 亜空砲『Δスタッフ』

dictionary.description: A goddess of another world with advanced mechanical technology. In order to establish a system of perfect order, she plotted to engulf the entire world in machinery. She worked in secret to destroy a goddess who opposed her ideal, until the appearance of a certain weapon of mass destruction turned the tides of war. Both of the deities she had persuaded into working with her were destroyed. She then settled on the introduction of new technology as a means of overcoming this difficulty. In order to obtain this technology, she sent the souls of the defeated gods to another world.
dictionary.fusion:
You irrational and pitiful fools…
Your ignorance will end this world.
Surrender before it's too late…
dictionary.summon:
I die, and the world dies…
Must I do your bidding
as long as I fail to crumble?

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を２０％アップ
leader skill.name: 覇王の力

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１３連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ・確率でスパーククリティカルが発生＆味方のＢＢゲージを超絶増加
bb.name: 亜空層『Σレイヤー』

dictionary.description: When the souls of two dead gods were summoned from another world, she used that opportunity to descend to Elgaia herself. There she began her search for new technologies immediately, and discovered many. Among them was Summoning, a technique created by the gods of that world, which she found particularly inspiring. However, as she went about her search, she encountered three Summoners. She fled immediately, sensing that these were powerful beings, but soon encountered another goddess from her home world.
dictionary.evolution:
Elgaia…
The system is false here, too.
I shall evolve, if I can…
dictionary.fusion:
Summoning makes humans
even more foolish…
Those Summoners were cursed beings,
even more so than others…
dictionary.summon:
Human-loving and hating goddesses…
What does each destroy, or save?
In the end, there is always ruin.

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を４０％アップ＆スパークダメージを７５％アップ
leader skill.name: 畏限妃の冥力

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１６連ダメージ（連続発動で威力をアップ）＆ターン終了時に強力な追加ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ・確率でスパーククリティカルが発生＆自分のＢＢゲージを満タンにする
sbb.name: ファスト・デコヒーレンス

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１４連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をかなりアップ・確率でスパーククリティカルが発生＆味方のＢＢゲージを超絶増加
bb.name: 亜空歪崩『Φリージョン』

dictionary.description: Malbelle recognized upon meeting the other goddess that their existences were incompatible. Immediately afterwards, a battle between the two began and ended with their simultaneous destruction. The three Summoners who visited the site of the battle afterwards and investigated her remains told of finding a technique she had developed. This technique allowed for the infinite replication of real souls. The records she left would go on to play a key role in the completion of Mock Units, but that is a tale to be told at a later time.
dictionary.evolution:
Truths are unnecessary…
Falsehoods are also unnecessary…
Simply make me stronger.
dictionary.fusion:
My legacy has made humanity
even more foolish…
Am I more foolish still?
dictionary.summon:
She and I are two sides of a coin…
Beings that must never meet.
Our chance meeting was our doom.

extra skill.desc: ＨＰが満タン時、攻撃力をかなりアップ＆ＢＢゲージが満タン時、攻撃力をアップ
extra skill.name: 残された記録の価値

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を８０％アップ＆スパークダメージを１００％アップ
leader skill.name: 畏限闇妃の冥葬力

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１８連ダメージ（連続発動で威力をアップ）＆ターン終了時に強力な追加ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をかなりアップ・確率でスパーククリティカルが発生＆自分のＢＢゲージを満タンにする
sbb.name: インテグラ・デコヒーレンス

ubb.name: ディヴァイド・パラドクス

bb.name: 執着セシ愛情ト悪意

leader skill.name: 死神に愛された妹

bb.name: デッドラブムーン

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を７０％アップ＆低確率で呪い状態にする＆被ダメージ時、確率でＨＰを回復
leader skill.name: 妹ポテンシャル

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１８連ダメージ＆３ターン、ターン終了時に追加ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ
sbb.name: 妹黒変化

bb.desc: 敵単体に強力な闇属性１２連ダメージ＆３ターン、自分のＢＢゲージを超絶増加
bb.name: ブラッドラミナ

dictionary.description: A wielder of shadow arms, and the sixth imperial princess of Bariura when the empire faced the wrath of the gods. Like the eighth imperial princess, she was given martial training from a very young age, but unlike her sister, she showed great enthusiasm. Melina was mainly trained for infiltration and assassination missions. Earning praise from her father with each accomplishment, this innocent child soon mastered the art of assassination. However, it's said that this greatly troubled the heart of her favorite uncle.
dictionary.fusion:
I think I got a bit stronger!
Uncle Chrome's gonna be thrilled to hear about this!
dictionary.summon:
Oh, so you're my target?
What! Oh, really?
You're the one who summoned me?
Then tell me, where's the target?

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を２０％アップ
leader skill.name: 覇王の力

bb.desc: 敵単体に強力な闇属性１５連ダメージ＆３ターン、自分のＢＢゲージを超絶増加
bb.name: フォルターラミナ

dictionary.description: Melina's role of gathering intelligence during infiltration missions gave her connections with various organizations throughout the Empire. Supposedly, she was in touch with prominent figures such as her uncle, the commissioner of the secret army, as well as a dark magician in charge of all the empire's magicians, and the former commander of the imperial knights. As such, she was familiar with the inner workings of not only the nations she infiltrated, but the Bariura Empire as well, including the personal information of many people. She was rightfully feared by many, not only for her role as a master assassin, but for the secrets she possessed.
dictionary.evolution: He he, these new toys must be for me? Now who am I gonna play with?
dictionary.fusion:
He he, I'm even stronger than ever!
I wonder what Elza will think when she sees me next!
dictionary.summon:
The farmer grows crops.
The blacksmith makes tools.
And the assassin kills people.
That's all there is to it!

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を４０％アップ＆ＢＢ発動に必要なＢＢゲージ量を軽減
leader skill.name: 煉血神の闇刃

sbb.desc: 敵単体に強力な闇属性２０連ダメージ（連続発動で威力をアップ）＆確率で攻撃力を１ターン大幅に低下＆高確率で怪我・弱体状態にする＆自分のＢＢゲージを満タンにする
sbb.name: エクスティンクション

bb.desc: 敵単体に強力な闇属性１７連ダメージ＆３ターン、自分のＢＢゲージを超絶増加
bb.name: サマエルイーター

dictionary.description: After the outbreak of war with the gods, records about Melina become extremely scarce. According to rare eyewitness accounts, it's been established for certain that she worked together with the first imperial princess. One theory is that she vanished together with her uncle, who had tried to kill the second and sixth imperial princesses. Many of the theories are contradictory, but they all have one point in common; Melina is seen laughing, covered in the blood of gods. Cool-headed and never clouded by thoughts of malice, she always had her blades ready for the next target.
dictionary.evolution:
Ahahahaha!
You're my best friend ever.
Let's go play some more!
dictionary.fusion:
Thanks for everything!
And don't worry!
I promise I love you, too!
dictionary.summon: You know, very scary people are hard to kill. It's pretty simple. I wonder why nobody else has figured it out?

extra skill.desc: ＢＢゲージが満タン時、攻撃力を大幅にアップ
extra skill.name: 悪意無く彷徨う血刃

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力を８０％アップ＆ＢＢ発動に必要なＢＢゲージ量をかなり軽減＆被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
leader skill.name: 煉血純神の葬刃

sbb.desc: 敵単体に強力な闇属性２１連ダメージ（連続発動で威力をアップ）＆確率で攻撃力を１ターン大幅に低下＆高確率で怪我・弱体状態にする＆自分のＢＢゲージを満タンにする
sbb.name: ラストエクスティンクション

ubb.name: ディミオス

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１２連ダメージ＆確率でスパークダメージ耐性を２ターン低下＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ
bb.name: ドライスカージ

extra skill.name: 色々と期待できる素材

leader skill.name: 彷徨える神魂

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１８連ダメージ＆確率でスパークダメージ耐性を２ターン低下＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ・攻撃力をかなりアップ
sbb.name: マギナインベイジョン

ubb.desc: 敵全体に超強力な闇属性２１連ダメージ＆スパークダメージ耐性を３ターンかなり低下＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力を大幅にアップ・攻撃力を超絶アップ
ubb.name: 冥崩儀『ネビロステラー』

bb.name: アビスレイヴ

dictionary.description: A mock Unit based on Ark, a disciple of Lucius. After sealing away Karna Masta, he chose to follow Lucius in exchange for the life of the Oracle Maiden, Ilia. In becoming Lucius's disciple, his strength increased and he was granted a longer lifespan than that of the average human. Unfortunately, it is said that once this occurred he lost the ability to live up to his true potential. Upon meeting a certain Summoner and goddess, however, he regained the hope that he had once cast aside.
dictionary.fusion:
It was so easy to just quit...
At some point I stopped moving forward. You're the reason I could walk again.
dictionary.summon:
I know...
I know how heavy my sin is...
I'll keep on living in spite of it!

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの全能力を２５％アップ＆スパーク時、ＢＣ出現率をかなりアップ・スパークダメージを５０％アップ
leader skill.name: 冥業神の命罪

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性３２連ダメージ＆確率で攻撃力・防御力を１ターン大幅に低下＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力をかなりアップ

In becoming Lucius's disciple, his strength increased and he was granted a longer lifespan than that of the average human. Unfortunately, it is said that once this occurred he lost the ability to live up to his true potential. Upon meeting a certain Summoner and goddess, however, he regained the hope that he had once cast aside.
dictionary.fusion:
It was so easy to just quit...
At some point I stopped moving forward. You're the reason I could walk again.

I know...
I know how heavy my sin is...
I'll keep on living in spite of it!

sbb.name: 滅界の剣『ベルフェリアス』

ubb.desc: イリアの加護により聖剣と化したアークの双剣は、大神皇カルナ・マスタの力をも抑えこむ
ubb.name: 封神の聖剣『ディムグリス』

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１４連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、ＢＣ獲得時の増加量をアップ・ターン毎にＢＢゲージをかなり増加・スパーク時、ＢＢゲージを少し増加
bb.name: ヴェイカント・リフト

dictionary.description: A disciple of the god Kulyuk, one of the Divine Ten. Zeal disliked interacting with others and always wore a mask to keep his distance, but did jump to the occasion when a chance to serve Kulyuk presented itself. He was regarded as quite the talented disciple thanks to his great agility and stealth, which were perfect for conducting the secret missions his master usually entrusted him with. Although Zeal usually avoided the battlefield during his missions, he did wield a double edged spear made of an unknown material when he had no choice but to fight. Legend has it he displayed incredible strength in battle.
dictionary.fusion:
If you are strengthening me, it must
mean my own power doesn't suffice.
I will remember that...
dictionary.summon:
My identity is no business of yours.
Now hurry.
Give me your orders.

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ
leader skill.name: 覇王の霊力

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１８連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、ＢＣ獲得時の増加量をかなりアップ・ターン毎にＢＢゲージをかなり増加・スパーク時、ＢＢゲージを少し増加
bb.name: ヴェイカント・ゲイル

dictionary.description: When the Sealed God's influence in the World of the Gods began to rise, Zeal began to suspect that the order of that world had grown corrupted, and began conducting a secret investigation with his master's permission. His exact methods remain unknown, but Kulyuk did disappear almost immediately after Zeal uncovered some classified information regarding the Holy Emperor, and thus many believe the two actions to be linked to one another. No one knows if Zeal ever shared this information with his master and his other comrades, but once his master went missing, he continued operating on his own.
dictionary.evolution:
I do not fear change.
If I did, it would stunt my growth.
dictionary.fusion:
It is better to hide one's strength
than to show it off meaninglessly...
Regardless, steady training is still required.
dictionary.summon:
Keep your priorities in check.
If you lose yourself in the moment, you will waste a perfectly good plan..

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆攻撃ＢＢの威力をかなりアップ
leader skill.name: 冥秘神の閃禍

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性３０連ダメージ＆確率でスパークダメージ耐性を２ターン低下＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力をかなりアップ・攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ
sbb.name: 双煉のエニグマ

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１９連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、ＢＣ獲得時の増加量をかなりアップ・ターン毎にＢＢゲージを大幅に増加・スパーク時、ＢＢゲージを少し増加
bb.name: ヴェイカント・クローズ

dictionary.description: One of the reasons speculated as to why Zeal chose to move on his own was because he didn't want to compromise any of his comrades by exposing them to confidential information. Eventually he would be ambushed by one of the Sealed God's disciples, and in their heated battle, a gate to another world opened, causing them both to disappear. Legends that tell of this particular encounter state that he fought in his master's name until the very end, displaying power far beyond that of any average disciple.
dictionary.evolution:
I don't need anyone's understanding.
I only need the strength to pierce my own will. Just like that person I used to serve...
dictionary.fusion:
This power...
I won't fight from the shadows any longer. After all, we both seem to have enemies we must face.
dictionary.summon:
Useless information is worthless.
Just leave it all to me.
I will fight now...on equal terms!

extra skill.desc: ＢＢ及びＳＢＢに「味方全体に３ターン、ＢＣ・ＨＣ出現率をかなりアップ」を追加
extra skill.name: 破滅を招く機密

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力・最大ＨＰを４０％アップ＆攻撃ＢＢの威力を大幅にアップ＆スパーク時、ＢＢゲージを増加
leader skill.name: 終冥崩神の殲禍

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性４０連ダメージ＆確率でスパークダメージ耐性を２ターン低下＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力をかなりアップ・攻撃ＢＢの威力をかなりアップ
sbb.name: 双冥のエニグマ

ubb.desc: 敵全体に超強力な闇属性２５連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力を超絶アップ・スパークダメージを超絶アップ・クリティカルダメージを超絶アップ・スパーク時、ＢＢゲージを超絶増加
ubb.name: ロスト・アナザー

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１０連ダメージ＆味方のＢＢゲージを増加
bb.name: マッスルパンチ

dictionary.description: A god from another world who is said to have once stood above all other divinities. Dagda would eventually meet a Hunter cadet in the underworld after the young man had suffered a mortal wound, and ultimately strike a pact with him. The young man accepted Dagda's offer without understanding what the demon meant by calling him "Godslayer" in order to gain back his life. Dagda would then rise to a world in ruin with the young Hunter to enter the heat of battle.
dictionary.fusion:
If it is power that you seek,
present me with more energy.
This too is your responsibility.
dictionary.summon:
If you wish to make a pact with me, then state your name.
Will you do as I ask?

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力・最大ＨＰを２０％アップ＆与ダメージが一定数を超える度に３ターン、攻撃力をアップ
leader skill.name: 神殺しを生みし神

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１２連ダメージ＆味方のＢＢゲージをかなり増加＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃時、確率でＨＰを少し吸収
bb.name: エナジードレイン

dictionary.description: A god from another world who is said to have once stood above all other divinities. As the war between demons and angels waged in his world, a polytheistic faction arose and declared war as well. However, Dagda did not join their ranks, instead seeking to put his own plans into motion. He would slay the gods as he had promised, destroy the monotheistic gods, and much more. The young man he had chosen would go on to forge many friendships, carving a great number of bonds and claiming a multitude of victories in the process. However, the ultimate outcome of all this remains to be seen.
dictionary.evolution:
Nature is nature...
Man is man...
It is as the world should be.
dictionary.fusion: Did you not also receive your power from the gods? Humans are complicated creatures indeed.
dictionary.summon: It would seem you are not the god-killer I seek. Regardless, you shall do my bidding.

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆与ダメージが一定数を超える度にＢＢゲージを大幅に増加・３ターン、攻撃力をアップ
leader skill.name: 世界の在りようを問う

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１６連ダメージ（連続発動で威力をアップ）＆味方全体に３ターン、クリティカル率を大幅にアップ・クリティカルダメージを少しアップ
sbb.name: ディナイアル

bb.desc: 味方全体のＨＰを大回復＆味方のＢＢゲージをかなり増加＆味方全体に３ターン、全状態異常を無効・攻撃に光・闇属性を付与＆１ターン、攻撃力・防御力・回復力を低下する効果を無効
bb.name: キュアスクリーン

dictionary.description: One of the founding members of the Guardians of Meirith. Born to a long line of magicians, she was required to undergo brutal training in order to master an enormous volume of knowledge and techniques. It is said she did all of this without ever once acknowledging the strain. She was beloved by many for her honest, open personality and abilities, but it is said that some also held the opposite opinion. When she was eventually asked to join the Guardians directly by disciples of the Holy Emperor, she did so gladly.
dictionary.fusion:
I don't like fighting...
But I will do my best,
to ensure everyone's happiness.
dictionary.summon: I'm honored to be Summoned by a renowned Summoner... I will do my absolute best.

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆ターン毎にＨＰを少し回復
leader skill.name: 統神の天啓

bb.desc: 味方全体のＨＰを大回復＆味方のＢＢゲージを大幅に増加＆味方全体に３ターン、全状態異常を無効・攻撃に光・闇属性を付与＆１ターン、攻撃力・防御力・回復力を低下する効果を無効
bb.name: キュアスケイプ

dictionary.description: In the beginning, she used her talents without hesitation in order to slay demons as one of the Guardians. However, it is also believed that her relationships with some of her comrades were poor, on account of her pride at having been directly selected by the gods. This eventually came to the point of betting leadership of the group on a mock battle between herself and the swordswoman who led the Guardians at the time. The battle is said to have been intense, but no records remain of the outcome, or of the winner.
dictionary.evolution:
I seem to have gained new power...
This much is nothing out of the ordinary for a Guardian such as myself.
dictionary.fusion:
I still have far to go.
I must grow stronger...stronger than her.
dictionary.summon:
She's our leader.
So, she has to be stronger than me, right...? Oh, never mind, it's nothing.

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆ターン毎にＨＰを少し回復・ＢＢゲージを増加
leader skill.name: 冥法神の天啓

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１２連ダメージ＆ＯＤゲージを少し増加＆味方全体に３ターン、ターン毎にＨＰを大回復・攻撃に光・闇属性を付与・ＯＤゲージ増加量をかなりアップ
sbb.name: ティラーリング

bb.desc: 味方全体のＨＰを大回復＆味方のＢＢゲージを超絶増加＆味方全体に３ターン、全状態異常を無効・攻撃に光・闇属性を付与＆１ターン、攻撃力・防御力・回復力を低下する効果を無効
bb.name: キュアフォールド

dictionary.description: After the mock battle for leadership of the Guardians, she began to display an aggressive personality and behavior unlike her previous self. It is said that a warning from the swordswoman led to this, but according to analysis by some historians this was actually her true personality. It is unclear what sort of change occurred in her, but she went on to make great achievements in both her role as a Guardian and in magical research. Eventually, her descendants would go on to join Meirith in later generations.
dictionary.evolution:
Oh, come on!
Enough already!
Being a good girl is bad for my skin!
dictionary.fusion:
Not yet, my limit's still far off!
More power, please!
I love to fight!
dictionary.summon: Everyone loved me when I was a good girl. But she told me not to smile when I didn't mean it. What an idiot, seriously.

extra skill.desc: ＢＢ及びＳＢＢに「味方全体の全状態異常を回復」を追加＆全状態異常を無効
extra skill.name: 異才の血統

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの最大ＨＰを５０％アップ＆ターン毎にＨＰを回復・ＢＢゲージをかなり増加＆ＯＤゲージの増加量をかなりアップ
leader skill.name: 冥穹神の天導告

60976.name: 閃麗の冥天神エクリス

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１８連ダメージ＆ＯＤゲージを少し増加＆味方全体に３ターン、ターン毎にＨＰを大回復・攻撃に光・闇属性を付与・ＯＤゲージ増加量をかなりアップ
sbb.name: アルシェループ

ubb.desc: 敵全体に超強力な闇属性２３連ダメージ＆味方全体に高確率で一度だけ戦闘不能を耐える効果を付与＆３ターン、ターン毎にＨＰを全回復・ＢＢゲージを超絶増加・ＯＤゲージ増加量を超絶アップ
ubb.name: カリ・ユガの冥祈

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性６連ダメージ＆確率で攻撃力・防御力を１ターン低下＆味方のＢＢゲージを増加＆味方全体に３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージを増加
bb.name: 霊騎士『マーネス』

dictionary.description: One of the women who served the goddess Felice, a member of the Divine Ten. As a necromancer she would harvest the spirits of warriors from old battlefields and began working under Felice due to the urging of her two sisters. She showed no interest at first, but after meeting a certain girl, she began working for the goddess. It is said her actions came not from faith, but from an interest in the dragons owned by the girl.
dictionary.fusion:
I see, so this is fusion.
It's a skill just as horrible and splendid as my necromancy.
dictionary.summon:
Do you know where souls go to?
I'll take you there just this once...

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの防御力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ
leader skill.name: 絶神の聖域

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性８連ダメージ＆確率で攻撃力・防御力を１ターン低下＆味方のＢＢゲージをかなり増加＆味方全体に３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
bb.name: 霊騎鎧『アタナトイ』

dictionary.description: While helping her sisters work for the goddess, she furthered her study of necromancy and strengthened her skills. Her arts made the followers uncomfortable, but she never paid any mind to the opinions of others. In their time together, she deepened her relationship with the girl favored by the goddess, continuing to study her dragons. It is said that the goddess was shocked when she discovered her research papers, but ultimately only showed a sorrowful expression.
dictionary.evolution: It's been a while, so I suppose I should help my sisters. I've found something very interesting as well.
dictionary.fusion: I'll accept your assistance with thanks. And if you're so inclined, you could always offer up your soul to me.
dictionary.summon:
Normally,
no matter how close they are,
two souls never become one.
But what about them...?

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの防御力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆通常攻撃ＨＩＴ数を増加
leader skill.name: 屍魂神の霊域

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１２連ダメージ＆確率で呪い状態にする＆確率で攻撃力・防御力を１ターンかなり低下＆味方全体に３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加・確率でＨＰを少し回復
sbb.name: エンスレイブ・アニムス

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１３連ダメージ＆確率で攻撃力・防御力を１ターン大幅に低下＆味方のＢＢゲージを大幅に増加＆味方全体に３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加
bb.name: 秘霊獄騎『ゴドフロワ』

dictionary.description: When the news of the goddess's death reached them, her sisters tried to ascertain the facts and where the girl who supposedly killed her went, but she herself didn't participate. When asked if she knew of the girl's whereabouts, she would simply answer that she was in a place they could not go, and would speak no more. Later, it is said she parted ways with her sisters and left for places unknown.
dictionary.evolution:
Everything eventually sinks
into the abyss...
Was this also the hand of fate?
Even I...don't know the answer...
dictionary.fusion:
I could never make anyone happy
with my research...
Could fusion do that?
dictionary.summon:
Searching is useless.
Following is useless.
All lies in the depths of darkness,
where even I cannot see...

extra skill.desc: 確率で防御貫通効果を付与＆クリティカルを無効＆確率で２回まで戦闘不能を耐える
extra skill.name: 深淵に送る言の葉

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの防御力・最大ＨＰを４０％アップ＆通常攻撃ＨＩＴ数を増加＆確率で通常攻撃を全体攻撃化する
leader skill.name: 屍淵神の霊魂域

60986.name: 霊刻の溟貴神ミゼルカ

sbb.desc: 敵全体に強力な闇属性１７連ダメージ＆高確率で呪い状態にする＆確率で攻撃力・防御力を１ターン大幅に低下＆味方全体に３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージをかなり増加・確率でＨＰを少し回復
sbb.name: ヴァーサレッジ・アニムス

ubb.desc: 敵全体に超強力な闇属性２２連ダメージ＆攻撃力・防御力を３ターン超絶低下＆味方全体の最大ＨＰを大幅にアップ＆３ターン、被ダメージ時、ＢＢゲージを超絶増加・ＨＰを超絶回復
ubb.name: サーカムフュージョン

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１５連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃ＢＢの威力を少しアップ・全属性の弱点属性ダメージを少しアップ
bb.name: パッ破！！！

leader skill.desc: 残りＨＰが多いほど、攻撃力をアップ＆攻撃ＢＢの威力をアップ
leader skill.name: 最強の超能力少年

bb.desc: 敵全体に闇属性１１連ダメージ＆味方全体に３ターン、攻撃力を大幅にアップ・攻撃ＢＢの威力をかなりアップ・全属性の弱点属性ダメージをアップ・攻撃時、確率でＨＰを少し吸収
bb.name: ケイオス・スクイーズ

dictionary.description: A mock Unit modeled after Kalon, the Heresy Demon. Kalon was known in Ishgria as a terrifying demon with the ability to divide his incredible power into multiple parts. However, after meeting a certain Oracle Maiden, he ceased any unnecessary displays of power, and took it upon himself to use his powers to protect the world of Ishgria. Rumor has it that his new course of action was influenced by the Oracle Maiden's self-sacrifice.
dictionary.fusion: Real strength is not born from power. It is because I lived without a purpose for so long that I can now see the true value of things.
dictionary.summon:
A human has managed to summon me...?
Very well. If your will is as powerful as hers was, I shall serve you.

extra skill.desc: ＨＰが半分以上の時、攻撃ＢＢの威力をかなりアップ
extra skill.name: 希望を継ぐ力

leader skill.desc: 全てのユニットの攻撃力・最大ＨＰを３０％アップ＆攻撃ＢＢの威力を超絶アップ＆確率でスパーククリティカルが発生
leader skill.name: 導黒神の封翼

dictionary.description: Although Kalon ultimately chose to protect the world of Ishgria, many claim that his past links him to many demons who may have played a hand in the heated battle he fought against his younger brother. He is also said to have sealed most of his younger sibling's power away during the same fight. Had he succumbed to his true nature as a demon, Kalon would have most likely incited wars in the regions he ruled, seeking to further expand his territory. There is no doubt that the demon world would have witnessed even more chaos at his hands.
dictionary.evolution:
Is my power what you seek?
Allow me to offer a demonstration...
You shall learn the ruin and chaos born of demons!
dictionary.fusion: Do not assume that I will serve you in exchange for power. A demon would never do such a thing.
dictionary.summon:
Fighting and scheming...
That is the essence of Ishgria.
I am no more than that myself.

dictionary.description: A Mock Unit of Rahnas, commander and founder of the "Abel Faction." The Faction is an Elgaia Federation organization dedicated to secretly gathering information on other worlds, and is said to be the only group capable of opposing the Akras Summoners' Hall. Similarly, Rahnas is rumored to have strong ties to the Summoners of Old. Although this Unit's skills in command and battle are both undeniable, it is thought to fall far short of Rahnas's true power due to the scarcity of the information it was based around.
dictionary.fusion: Heh... I wondered what you were up to, but to think a gutless dog of the Summoners' Hall would try to toughen me up! Ridiculous!
dictionary.summon: Making copies of me will not bode well. A perfect example of the Summoners' Hall's cowardly thinking and technology.

dictionary.description: Although it operates under extreme secrecy at present, the Abel Faction is said to wield major influence over both the military and politics of the Elgaia Federation. As its commander, he would likely transform the Elgaia Federation into a mighty nation if given sole authority to lead. This would likely be achieved by limiting civil liberties and managing the military, political, and economic balance of the land. Any nation he built would definitely pose a fearsome threat to the Randall Empire and Akras Summoners' Hall.
dictionary.evolution: Absolute rule of the Federation is just the beginning. It's just a natural stepping stone for the completion of my true goals.
dictionary.fusion: Very well, I will use you. For a member of the faceless masses, you seem a fairly useful sort.
dictionary.summon: Grahdens, Owen...and all you pathetic Summoners. I will give you the barest glimpse of my power!

dictionary.description: A sorcerer who sought to claim the treasure of a certain kingdom in Grand Gaia. Gregor plotted the kidnapping of the nation's princess in order to get his hands on the treasure, but his plans were foiled when a certain knight under the princess's service reached out to a famous thief for help. He then decided to retaliate by sending his army to attack the small nation, hoping to destroy it with his dark magic. However, legend claims Gregor was the one to meet his destruction instead once the princess attained the hidden powers of the treasure he had coveted so.
dictionary.fusion:
It would seem you know your place.
Very good.
Now bring me more power!
dictionary.summon: A fool like you has summoned me here? Then I shall reward you by making you a device in my plans...

dictionary.description: Gregor is known for his obsession with obtaining the royal treasure of a certain nation, and fueling that obsession was the unsurmountable amount of research he had conducted on its hidden powers. According to some of the recorded data he left behind, the treasure's powers would turn its wielder into a demon. Had he been able to get his hands on the royal jewel and unleashed its full potential, he would've achieved his ideal physical form as a demon. He would have then used his new powers to his heart's content in order to strike fear throughout the whole of Grand Gaia.
dictionary.evolution:
It would seem my research was on the right track.
Mwa ha ha ha...
This power shall make me invincible!
dictionary.fusion:
No one else can rival me now.
I have no need for more power.
I shall accept sacrifices, however...
dictionary.summon:
So this is the jewel's power...
I shall begin my retribution by crushing that insolent thief!

dictionary.description: Daughter of a half-lion, half-divine demon. Rescued by an assassin that served her father as her clan was annihilated in an ambush by the dragon demon clan, she swore to have her vengeance. She targeted the dragon demon clan leader's child relentlessly, and even set out on a journey for Grand Gaia. However, a warrior from the dragon demon clan awaited her there. The two are believed to have fought a savage battle, but its outcome remains unknown. All traces of her vanish following the battle, while tales hold that the daughter of the dragon clan's leader was granted protection by an Elder Summoner.
dictionary.fusion:
Father's grudges, and my clan's...
I'll take any means of avenging them. Just keep giving me more power!
dictionary.summon: I don't care who or what you are... If you're fighting against those worthless dragons, then I'm glad to help you out!

dictionary.description: Viktor is said to have cared deeply for his clan, and as his daughter, many interpret her vendetta against the dragon demon clan leader's child as having been born from the same love of her people. Had she chosen the recovery of her clan over vengeance, she likely would have worked passionately to restore their power and overcome any obstacles in her way. She also might have grown into a force that even Barion could not afford to take lightly, and posed a significant threat to the dragon demon clan.
dictionary.evolution: My hatred for the dragons hasn't faded... But there are other things I have to do. Paying my debts...will come right after that!
dictionary.fusion: I said to give me all the power you can, didn't I? It's fine, I understand... I'm definitely going to drive those dragons to the brink!
dictionary.summon:
He had a violent side,
but Father was always nice to me and the clan... I know that much.

dictionary.description: The most trusted staff officer of the Randall Empire's first emperor. Identifying the emperor's talents before his rise, Johan spread word that he was the descendant of a hero who had led the people of Elgaia, which helped win unprecedented support. After the empire's founding, Johan laid the foundations for its government and the current system of aristocracy. However, he also set about permanently eliminating all obstacles to his own personal ideals, and even attempted to execute the decorated leader of the volunteer army. This earned him widespread animosity, and he was assassinated by an unknown individual with his ambitions still unfulfilled.
dictionary.fusion: This technique for using talented people... It's so logical, so breathtaking! There's a lesson in government to be learned from this.
dictionary.summon: It seems our interests are aligned. I will keep getting my hands dirty in order to form a perfect nation!

dictionary.description: Skilled in combat despite being a civil official, he took up arms and fought in the war for unification. As a result, the commander of the imperial guard was never hostile even when needing to rein him in, and he made substantial improvements to the nation's power. Opinions on his policies are divided, but his passionate dedication to the empire was indisputable. A true, complete unification of Elgaia might have been possible had he lived to see his ideal nation made a reality.
dictionary.evolution: My dream is eternal prosperity for the empire... I will share the glory of the emperor with all of Elgaia!
dictionary.fusion:
Heh, it seems like you get it.
This thriving empire is proof that I was correct!
dictionary.summon: Cringing at mere criticism is despicable. Scum who lose themselves over others' views cannot rule a nation!
